Class MapViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.arch.lifecycle.ViewModel
      • bean.pwr.imskamieskiego.view_models.MapViewModel

  • public class MapViewModel
extends android.arch.lifecycle.ViewModel
    View model which contain actual selected start point, targets and route. This view model is created for preserving data for MapDrawer between orientation changes etc.
